Full Title: Lengua y Migración 


Linguistic Field(s): Sociolinguistics 

Call Deadline: 30-Sep-2009 

Papers and book reviews are welcome for the Journal 'Lengua y migración'
(Language and Migration).

Lengua y migración (Language and Migration) publishes original,
theoretical, empirical and methodological papers about linguistic and
communicative reality of migration, taking care of social and linguistic
elements in the process of sociolinguistic integration, including
acquisition of second languages.

Lengua y migración (Language and Migration) publishes papers and book
reviews about sociolinguistic and sociological aspects related to the
migratory processes in any region or community of the world.

Lengua y migración (Language and Migration) publishes papers of different
linguistic specialties: sociolinguistic and sociology of the language,
descriptive linguistics, pragmatics, discourse analyses, conversational
analyses and other matters interested by the use of the language in
migration contexts. The journal leaves space for intercultural and
cross-cultural studies as long as they have migration as an object.

Lengua y migración (Language and Migration) publishes papers and book
reviews in Spanish and English.

Call Deadline: 30-Sep-2009




